b'{"data_headers":{"result_code":1},"data":{"information":{"article_id":2220,"category_name":"News","pr_category_id":"1","title_name":"Regarding Issues with the Descriptions of Certain Adventurer Skills","message":"<div>Since the release of version 2.4.0, we have identified the following issues with the text descriptions in the details of certain adventurers. These issues only affect the text itself and have now been resolved.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>As a token of our appreciation for your patience, we will send 120 wyrmite to all players who started playing before <span class=\\"local_date\\" data-local_date=\\"1621835999\\"><\/span>. This gift can be claimed from your goodie box for up to seven days after reception.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe skill description text for the adventurer Gala Alex&#39;s skills Umbral Erasure Lv. 1 and Umbral Erasure Lv. 2 incorrectly lists Skill Energy Required as 2,120. The correct value is 1,129.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe skill description text for the adventurer Gala Mym&#39;s skill Dragon Claw incorrectly lists Dragon Energy Gained as 150. The correct value is 50.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>\\u30fbThe skill description text for the adventurer Gala Mym&#39;s skill Dragon Claw Lv. 3 incorrectly lists Skill Energy Required (Shared Skill) as 6,702. The correct value is 12,821.<\/div><div><br><\/div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.<\/div>","start_time":1621836000,"prev_article_id":"2178","next_article_id":"2209","image_path":"","update_time":1621588884}}}'